1
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:03,560
I suddenly miss Liu Heng so much.

2
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:04,239
Huh?

3
00:01:04,799 --> 00:01:06,120
Why would you miss Liu Heng?

4
00:01:06,879 --> 00:01:07,920
This way, please.

5
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:25,920
These two...

6
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,480
I'll take them.

7
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:31,280
Know why I let you two out?

8
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:31,959
No idea.

9
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,760
You want us to help you kill Liu Jun, right?

10
00:01:34,799 --> 00:01:35,599
Ah!

11
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:36,840
Clever.

12
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:38,680
Young lady.

13
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,000
I see you have impressive skills.

14
00:01:42,079 --> 00:01:43,319
I'd like to ask a favor of you.

15
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:48,040
Tomorrow, I'll invite him over.

16
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:49,879
When that happens,

17
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,159
you'll pose as a Dubian Kingdom assassin

18
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:55,599
and take his head.

19
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,079
Once it's done,

20
00:01:58,079 --> 00:02:01,480
I'll guarantee you both safety for life.

21
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:04,959
Who knew the Late Emperor in Imperial Uncle Liu's dream was such a vile schemer!

22
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,280
What did you say?

23
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:10,719
Oh, I said...

24
00:02:11,919 --> 00:02:12,400
Yes, no problem, we'll definitely help you.

25
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:13,520
I won't.

26
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,919
What are you doing?

27
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:15,719
Oh, come on!

28
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,560
You two are brothers.

29
00:02:17,919 --> 00:02:19,719
He bears you no ill will.

30
00:02:20,159 --> 00:02:23,719
Yet for your own gain, you'd take his head.

31
00:02:23,719 --> 00:02:25,159
How could you be so despicable?

32
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:28,120
I won't help such a vile scoundrel.

33
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,560
Are you stupid?

34
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:30,840
This is a dream.

35
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:31,840
Nobody actually dies.

36
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,879
Just give him one stab and be done with it.

37
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:34,080
No! I'm stupid, and I won't do it!

38
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,360
I just won't help, won't help.

39
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,960
You... you... you...

40
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:39,759
Fine.

41
00:02:40,439 --> 00:02:41,360
You can refuse.

42
00:02:42,719 --> 00:02:44,360
But I'll kill him myself.

43
00:02:44,719 --> 00:02:45,000
Huh?

44
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:48,719
Fine, go ahead and kill him.

45
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:49,800
It's not like...

46
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,439
Anyway, I'm not afraid.

47
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:55,919
Alright.

48
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:57,439
Then I won't kill him.

49
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,039
But I'll torture him bit by bit.

50
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,199
Guards!

51
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:04,120
Yes!

52
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:06,479
Slash his leg twenty times.

53
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,280
Each cut one inch deep.

54
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,479
Do not fail me.

55
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:13,439
Do it!

56
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:14,360
Hey, wait a minute!

57
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:16,560
You win.

58
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:18,879
I'll kill him.

59
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:22,039
Changed your mind that fast?

60
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:23,840
Even though I'm a scoundrel,

61
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:26,800
you're still willing to help?

62
00:03:29,919 --> 00:03:30,719
I'll help.

63
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,039
It's just a dream anyway.

64
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:35,080
I won't actually die.

65
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,800
If you really don't want to help, forget it.

66
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,639
I can take it.

67
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,360
Tell me.

68
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:39,560
How do we kill him?

69
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,520
You all may withdraw now.

70
00:03:43,599 --> 00:03:45,400
I have secrets to share with our two guests.

71
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:46,879
Yes, sir.

72
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,719
You two...

73
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:09,319
One willing to kill for the other,

74
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,039
and the other

75
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:12,560
willing to take twenty stabs for the other.

76
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:15,680
You two clearly have an unusual bond.

77
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:16,959
Isn't that right, Chicken Raiser?

78
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,879
Chicken Raiser?

79
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:20,560
Huh?

80
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,319
You're the Crown Prince!

81
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,959
Why, you sneaky Cartoonist!

82
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:25,360
Go to hell!

83
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,040
Hey!

84
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:28,439
You two

85
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:32,279
are definitely not just ordinary friends.

86
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,279
You two

87
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,759
must be

88
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,560
super, super close friends, right?

89
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,120
Ugh.

90
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:50,680
Hmm.

91
00:04:51,639 --> 00:04:52,600
You little rascal,

92
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,360
you've been living the good life.

93
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,720
Way better than us.

94
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,720
The moment we got in here,

95
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,000
we were either being hunted

96
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,680
or thrown in jail.

97
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,879
When I first got in,

98
00:05:02,879 --> 00:05:03,839
I was hiding everywhere too.

99
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:07,120
But everyone I met called me "Your Highness."

100
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,959
Then I figured out

101
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:10,959
they were mistaking me for my father.

102
00:05:11,079 --> 00:05:12,680
So I just played along.

103
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:13,839
Hey,

104
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:16,000
were you the one fighting with Imperial Uncle Liu that day?

105
00:05:16,279 --> 00:05:18,120
That was my father.

106
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:21,480
After their fight, he left town to clear his head.

107
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,199
Once he was gone,

108
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:24,639
I could swagger around impersonating him.

109
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,360
Hey,

110
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:29,920
since you look so much like your father,

111
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:34,360
why not pretend to be him and go talk some sense into him?

112
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:38,279
Convince Imperial Uncle Liu to stop clinging to this dream.

113
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:39,800
It's just about the throne, isn't it?

114
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,199
After all these years,

115
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:42,639
he's still hung up on it,

116
00:05:43,079 --> 00:05:44,920
reliving it over and over in a dream.

117
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,000
Isn't he exhausted?

118
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,439
Him staying in this dream

119
00:05:48,439 --> 00:05:50,160
has nothing to do with the throne.

120
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:51,959
You've looked into it?

121
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:52,279
Mm-hmm.

122
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:53,279
I investigated.

123
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,639
Every day Imperial Uncle Liu is here,

124
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:57,439
he spends nearly all his time

125
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,639
with that girl named Yue'er.

126
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,600
I heard from my father

127
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:04,000
that Imperial Uncle Liu had a consort called Yue'er,

128
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,160
one of his most beloved consorts.

129
00:06:06,959 --> 00:06:09,199
But she passed away years ago.

130
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,800
So my guess is,

131
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:13,759
the reason he refuses to wake from this dream

132
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:16,439
is that he can't bear to leave Yue'er behind.

133
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:19,360
Easy fix.

134
00:06:19,839 --> 00:06:23,040
Let's go hide this Yue'er girl.

135
00:06:23,639 --> 00:06:25,279
That way Imperial Uncle Liu can't find her,

136
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:26,319
he'll panic,

137
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,319
and then he'll wake up, right?

138
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:28,680
Hiding her won't do.

139
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:29,639
We have to kill her.

140
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:30,079
Huh?

141
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:30,519
And what's more,

142
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:32,079
you two have to do it in front of him.

143
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,279
Great idea.

144
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:38,360
Isn't that way too cruel?

145
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:42,680
Use your head and think about it.

146
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,800
Why do we need Imperial Uncle Liu to wake up?

147
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:49,839
To fight the Dubian Kingdom.

148
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:53,600
And what does he think we two are right now?

149
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,160
Assassins from the Dubian Kingdom.

150
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,120
Exactly.

151
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,720
Once we kill Yue'er,

152
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:03,279
he'll hate us to the bone.

153
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,439
And that kind of hatred

154
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:06,680
will burn deep into his very marrow.

155
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,879
After he wakes up,

156
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:09,680
we invite him to attack the Dubian Kingdom.

157
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,199
How could he refuse?

158
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:15,160
That makes sense!

159
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,399
We act tonight.

160
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,519
Right after we finish eating.

161
00:07:26,839 --> 00:07:27,160
Yue'er

162
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:27,600
Watch out!

163
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,319
Hmm.

164
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,600
Fourth Brother.

165
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:38,839
Calling on me this late...

166
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:39,759
What's going on?

167
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:40,800
Sixth Brother.

168
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,160
I have something important to tell you.

169
00:07:42,439 --> 00:07:43,360
Let's step aside for a word.

170
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,360
If it's about that thing from last time,

171
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,920
let's just drop it.

172
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,439
It's definitely not that.

173
00:07:53,439 --> 00:07:54,639
Just come with me.

174
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:03,240
Don't move!

175
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:04,360
Assassins!

176
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,240
Guards!

177
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,199
Catch the assassins!

178
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:08,319
Don't you dare touch Yue'er!

179
00:08:08,879 --> 00:08:10,160
I'll agree to anything you want!

180
00:08:10,319 --> 00:08:11,399
Heh, heh.

181
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:15,199
You've slain countless Dubian Kingdom soldiers.

182
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:15,839
You...

183
00:08:15,839 --> 00:08:17,800
What could you possibly offer me?

184
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,160
I want none of it.

185
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:21,879
Today, you'll taste the pain of losing a loved one.

186
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:23,160
Hmph.

187
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,439
I'm sorry.

188
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:26,360
Even though you're just an illusion,

189
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,279
I really can't bring myself to do it.

190
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,160
Yue'er!

191
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,639
Yue'er!

192
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,440
Don't die on me!

193
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:46,279
You bunch of beasts!

194
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:51,240
I, Liu Jun, swear

195
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:56,440
in this life, I'll slaughter every last person of the Dubian Kingdom

196
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:58,080
to avenge Yue'er.

197
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:04,000
Huh? What's going on?

198
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:04,840
We're about to succeed!

199
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,919
Wait a moment.

200
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,480
Yue'er.

201
00:09:09,759 --> 00:09:10,240
My Prince.

202
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:12,600
Yue'er isn't dead.

203
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:12,960
Hmm?

204
00:09:13,399 --> 00:09:14,200
She's right here with me.

205
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:17,639
Then who's this in my arms?

206
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:19,360
Oh.

207
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:19,799
Here's the thing.

208
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,279
I anticipated someone would harm Lady Yue'er.

209
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:24,840
So I swapped her out long ago.

210
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:29,120
The Yue'er in your arms is a body double wearing a human-skin mask.

211
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,279
Heh heh.

212
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,120
Yue'er!

213
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:35,840
Yue'er!

214
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,759
My Prince.

215
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:38,799
Yue'er!

216
00:09:39,919 --> 00:09:41,679
You scared me to death.

217
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:44,679
Yue'er.

218
00:09:51,399 --> 00:09:52,399
Then who are you?

219
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,799
Why are you helping me?

220
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,879
Who I am isn't important.

221
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:58,399
But...

222
00:09:58,399 --> 00:09:59,919
just remember this face of mine.

223
00:10:00,279 --> 00:10:01,120
Remember, my name is Liu Heng.

224
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:05,440
I'm extremely, extremely, extremely well-suited to be emperor.

225
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,919
From now on, wherever you go,

226
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:09,480
just nominate me to be emperor,

227
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,120
and that'll do it.

228
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:12,399
Alright.

229
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:12,879
Alright.

230
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:14,080
As for...

231
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:16,320
these two,

232
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:17,799
arrest them at once!

233
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,399
Guards!

234
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:21,960
Seize the assassins!

235
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,480
Why isn't anyone coming?

236
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:26,519
Guards, hurry!

237
00:10:26,519 --> 00:10:27,440
Liu Heng, you shameless wretch!

238
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,440
When did you sneak in here?

239
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,679
Arrest them, now!

240
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,440
Sorry to say,

241
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,879
right when you were plotting tonight.

242
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:34,360
Looks like

243
00:10:34,639 --> 00:10:35,679
we'll have to outsmart him.

244
00:10:37,679 --> 00:10:38,320
My Prince,

245
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:40,279
snap out of it.

246
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:42,320
Yue'er has been gone for years.

247
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,720
Wake up from this dream!

248
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:45,600
Hey!

249
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,639
Don't believe a word they say.

250
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,799
They're all liars.

251
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:48,600
My Prince,

252
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,360
you and Yue'er were married.

253
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:52,039
She has already become your Yue'er.

254
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:54,080
You lived happily together for many years.

255
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,559
But Yue'er is gone now.

256
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:56,519
Now,

257
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:58,000
don't linger in this dream any longer.

258
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,799
Stop running from reality, okay?

259
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:02,080
I don't believe it.

260
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:03,679
Yue'er isn't dead!

261
00:11:04,399 --> 00:11:05,200
Sixth Brother,

262
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,720
Yue'er truly is dead.

263
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,240
You're just in a dream right now.

264
00:11:11,039 --> 00:11:11,679
Even I

265
00:11:12,559 --> 00:11:14,240
am only an illusion in your dream.

266
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:14,759
Hey!

267
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:15,679
Don't believe them.

268
00:11:15,679 --> 00:11:16,919
They're all liars.

269
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:19,240
I've put up with you long enough!

270
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:19,960
Argh!

271
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:22,440
I will definitely return!

272
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:22,960
Sixth Brother,

273
00:11:24,799 --> 00:11:26,080
reality is cruel,

274
00:11:27,039 --> 00:11:28,519
but you must face it.

275
00:11:32,639 --> 00:11:33,559
Impossible.

276
00:11:36,519 --> 00:11:37,960
I don't believe it.

277
00:11:49,279 --> 00:11:50,080
Prince.

278
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:56,679
Imperial Uncle Liu.

279
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:00,919
Imperial Uncle Liu.

280
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,840
Who are you people?

281
00:12:06,679 --> 00:12:08,639
Why are you intruding on my dream?

282
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,240
I am the envoy, Qi Zhi.

283
00:12:10,279 --> 00:12:11,480
This is the Princess of Yan.

284
00:12:11,519 --> 00:12:13,320
And this is the Crown Prince.

285
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:17,879
Imperial Uncle.

286
00:12:17,879 --> 00:12:20,320
The Dubian Kingdom exploited the undefended border of our Daliang Kingdom

287
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,399
and sent troops to invade us.

288
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,679
Only you and your army can save the Daliang Kingdom now.

289
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:27,639
Please, Imperial Uncle Liu, lead the troops against them.

290
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,679
Why should I bother?

291
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:33,840
You are the Imperial Uncle of the Daliang Kingdom.

292
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,000
The kingdom is in peril.

293
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,440
Surely you can't just stand by and watch.

294
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,879
If the kingdom's in peril,

295
00:12:38,759 --> 00:12:40,919
then go find the Emperor of the Daliang Kingdom.

296
00:12:41,799 --> 00:12:44,120
Your father wanted the throne so badly back then.

297
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:44,759
What now?

298
00:12:44,759 --> 00:12:47,480
He can't even handle a little thing like this,

299
00:12:47,519 --> 00:12:48,840
and you come running to me?

300
00:12:50,919 --> 00:12:51,840
Imperial Uncle.

301
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:55,240
You've been lost in your dreams for months,

302
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,200
so you may not know yet.

303
00:12:58,799 --> 00:13:00,120
Father is no longer with us.

304
00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:03,159
Gone?

305
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,240
Dead?

306
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,080
That's impossible.

307
00:13:08,919 --> 00:13:10,600
Fourth Brother was always healthier than me.

308
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,960
How could he go before I did?

309
00:13:12,559 --> 00:13:13,200
Impossible.

310
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,159
Imperial Uncle Liu.

311
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:16,399
The Late Emperor did not die of illness.

312
00:13:16,399 --> 00:13:18,320
He may have been poisoned.

313
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,279
Who?

314
00:13:20,279 --> 00:13:21,200
Who dared to do such a thing?

315
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,039
We haven't found out yet.

316
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:24,440
But right after the Late Emperor passed,

317
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,960
the Dubian Kingdom launched a full-scale invasion.

318
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,559
I believe

319
00:13:27,559 --> 00:13:29,240
the Dubian Kingdom must be behind this.

320
00:13:30,519 --> 00:13:31,480
Fine.

321
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:33,559
Tomorrow, I'll lead my troops to war

322
00:13:33,559 --> 00:13:35,879
and meet the Dubian Kingdom on the battlefield.

323
00:13:36,039 --> 00:13:37,600
I'll beat them to a pulp,

324
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,360
capture their generals, and demand to know

325
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:41,679
who killed my Fourth Brother.

326
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,000
Imperial Uncle Liu,

327
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,039
this brotherly devotion

328
00:13:45,039 --> 00:13:46,320
fills me with admiration.

329
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:47,120
Hey.

330
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:47,759
Me?

331
00:13:47,759 --> 00:13:51,519
I can't stand that old emperor.

332
00:13:52,279 --> 00:13:53,519
Who cares if he lives or dies?

333
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,960
It's just that I haven't fought in years,

334
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,320
and I'm itching for a fight.

335
00:13:58,679 --> 00:13:59,240
Uh.

336
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,759
Twenty years ago, I

337
00:14:00,759 --> 00:14:03,840
beat the Dubian Kingdom to a pulp and sent them running.

338
00:14:05,399 --> 00:14:07,000
If I don't teach them a lesson now,

339
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,480
no one in the Dubian Kingdom, top to bottom,

340
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,279
will remember who Liu Jun is.

341
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,279
Prince!

342
00:14:17,279 --> 00:14:18,320
Prince!

343
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:18,639
Yue'er.

344
00:14:19,559 --> 00:14:20,559
Prince, don't leave.

345
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,399
Yue'er.

346
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,399
I've grown old.

347
00:14:27,159 --> 00:14:28,919
It doesn't matter.

348
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,879
I still recognize you.

349
00:14:29,879 --> 00:14:31,159
You are my Prince.

350
00:14:32,759 --> 00:14:33,559
Yue'er.

351
00:14:34,559 --> 00:14:36,240
I haven't had enough time with you.

352
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,759
Don't go.

353
00:14:41,519 --> 00:14:42,320
Prince.

354
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:43,960
As the saying goes,

355
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:46,879
"A peerless beauty is a treasure

356
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:48,559
found only once."

357
00:14:49,159 --> 00:14:50,919
Lady Yue'er treats you so well.

358
00:14:50,919 --> 00:14:51,879
If I were you,

359
00:14:51,879 --> 00:14:54,639
I'd never abandon her for some kingdom or empire.

360
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:56,240
I should've broken your arm just now.

361
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,080
Beat me to death, it won't change a thing.

362
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:57,919
Get back here.

363
00:14:58,879 --> 00:15:00,279
This is the Prince's own business.

364
00:15:00,279 --> 00:15:01,120
Who are you to interfere?

365
00:15:02,679 --> 00:15:03,480
Prince.

366
00:15:03,799 --> 00:15:04,840
Ask yourself.

367
00:15:05,679 --> 00:15:07,080
Lady Yue'er treats you so well.

368
00:15:07,279 --> 00:15:08,679
Can you really bear to leave her?

369
00:15:10,679 --> 00:15:11,480
Prince.

370
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:15,879
Yue'er.

371
00:15:17,039 --> 00:15:18,080
I won't leave.

372
00:15:19,679 --> 00:15:22,159
I'll stay here with you for the rest of my life.

373
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,159
Imperial Uncle,

374
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:30,360
Do you still remember

375
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,679
how you met Lady Yue'er?

376
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:32,799
Of course I remember.

377
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:35,960
When the Dubian Kingdom army massacred her village,

378
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:39,080
I saved her from a Dubian Kingdom soldier's blade.

379
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:43,879
That's right.

380
00:15:44,639 --> 00:15:45,879
I heard from my father, the Emperor,

381
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:48,679
that Lady Yue'er admired you most, Imperial Uncle.

382
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:52,080
Because you were a great hero defending the nation.

383
00:15:53,879 --> 00:15:55,039
But who would have ever imagined

384
00:15:55,679 --> 00:15:56,840
that a great hero,

385
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:57,879
in his old age,

386
00:15:58,480 --> 00:16:00,000
would drown in a wine-soaked dream and never wake.

387
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,080
Imperial Uncle Liu,

388
00:16:06,039 --> 00:16:06,759
right now,

389
00:16:06,759 --> 00:16:09,240
will you stay by this fake Yue'er

390
00:16:09,519 --> 00:16:10,799
and keep deceiving yourself,

391
00:16:10,879 --> 00:16:11,879
or step out

392
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:14,519
and become the hero Yue'er truly admired?

393
00:16:15,879 --> 00:16:16,799
The choice is yours.

394
00:16:17,399 --> 00:16:18,080
But I...

395
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,279
Forget it, Crown Prince.

396
00:16:19,279 --> 00:16:20,240
Let's just go.

397
00:16:21,799 --> 00:16:24,720
We'll find someone else to attack the Dubian Kingdom.

398
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,799
I'm afraid back then, Yue'er

399
00:16:27,519 --> 00:16:29,440
was wrong about you.

400
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:33,000
Wait a moment.

401
00:16:55,039 --> 00:16:55,759
Hmph hmph.

402
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:57,159
Heh heh.

403
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:57,799
Princess,

404
00:16:57,799 --> 00:16:59,240
I was wrong.

405
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,399
I'll never play emperor again.

406
00:17:00,399 --> 00:17:01,679
Just let me off, please.

407
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:03,919
You like drinking,

408
00:17:04,279 --> 00:17:05,039
you like dreaming.

409
00:17:05,039 --> 00:17:05,640
Don't like it?

410
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,680
You like coming into my dream to play, huh?

411
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,000
Come on,

412
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,960
drink, drink, drink!

413
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:11,880
Drink!

414
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:18,440
Hahaha!

415
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:25,440
This sword has fought beside me for years.

416
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:26,440
I hope it,

417
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:28,000
just like me,

418
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,599
hasn't grown old yet.

419
00:17:34,279 --> 00:17:36,079
You three have traveled from afar,

420
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:38,480
and I've yet to play the proper host.

421
00:17:39,079 --> 00:17:39,480
Tonight,

422
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:42,880
enjoy fine food and drink here.

423
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:44,680
Tomorrow at dawn,

424
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:46,319
I shall lead my troops to war,

425
00:17:46,839 --> 00:17:48,240
to face the army of the Dubian Kingdom.

426
00:17:50,039 --> 00:17:52,960
Many thanks to you three for your help.

427
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:53,759
Come,

428
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:55,400
let me toast you all.

429
00:17:58,480 --> 00:17:59,440
Little Princess,

430
00:18:04,759 --> 00:18:05,559
please.

431
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:12,640
Oh my.

432
00:18:12,839 --> 00:18:14,839
You know what,

433
00:18:15,119 --> 00:18:17,359
You and your son look quite alike.

434
00:18:18,799 --> 00:18:19,599
Hey.

435
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:23,400
Wonder if that nasty temper is the same too.

436
00:18:23,519 --> 00:18:25,559
Hahahaha!

437
00:18:27,039 --> 00:18:27,839
Imperial Uncle Liu,

438
00:18:28,359 --> 00:18:29,960
Since you're skilled in both letters and arms,

439
00:18:30,119 --> 00:18:32,440
And of legitimate royal blood,

440
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:36,319
Would you consider, after defeating the Dubian Kingdom,

441
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:38,720
coming back to inherit the throne?

442
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,359
What kind of talk is that?

443
00:18:42,359 --> 00:18:45,160
The throne shall of course go to the Crown Prince.

444
00:18:46,119 --> 00:18:47,160
Hold your tongue right now.

445
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:48,440
I'll pretend you said nothing.

446
00:18:48,960 --> 00:18:50,200
If you say it again,

447
00:18:50,839 --> 00:18:53,240
That'll be a beheading offense.

448
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:55,799
Imperial Uncle,

449
00:18:56,559 --> 00:18:58,200
To be honest,

450
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,920
I've already decided not to be emperor.

451
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:02,319
Huh?

452
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:07,599
Hahahaha!

453
00:19:07,599 --> 00:19:09,279
Oh my!

454
00:19:10,119 --> 00:19:12,440
Oh, Fourth Brother, Fourth Brother!

455
00:19:13,359 --> 00:19:14,119
Who would've thought

456
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:15,559
You raise a son

457
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,759
who flat-out refuses to be emperor!

458
00:19:18,440 --> 00:19:19,640
Hahahaha!

459
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:21,880
Hey,

460
00:19:23,039 --> 00:19:23,720
Let me ask you,

461
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:24,480
Huh?

462
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:25,839
When you told him

463
00:19:26,359 --> 00:19:28,680
you wanted to draw cartoons for life,

464
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:32,119
Was he so angry his beard bristled?

465
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,200
You bet!

466
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:36,279
That beard stuck up

467
00:19:36,279 --> 00:19:37,200
This high!

468
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:39,160
Hahahaha!

469
00:19:39,400 --> 00:19:40,359
Hahaha!

470
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:42,839
Now that's perfect!

471
00:19:43,359 --> 00:19:44,519
Now if I die,

472
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:46,559
If I go down to the underworld,

473
00:19:46,559 --> 00:19:47,880
I'll have something to say.

474
00:19:48,480 --> 00:19:49,279
I'll ask him,

475
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:51,440
"Fourth Brother,

476
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:54,640
Your son doesn't want to be emperor.

477
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:56,519
What do you think of that?"

478
00:19:56,519 --> 00:19:57,079
Huh?

479
00:19:57,079 --> 00:19:59,079
Hahahaha!

480
00:19:59,079 --> 00:20:00,400
If you ask me,

481
00:20:00,559 --> 00:20:03,960
The throne belongs to no one but Imperial Uncle Liu.

482
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,759
Go to war right away.

483
00:20:05,759 --> 00:20:07,640
Come back after the war and take the throne.

484
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,160
Hey,

485
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:10,480
No, no.

486
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:12,759
Better

487
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:15,440
wait till after the war to talk about it.

488
00:20:15,759 --> 00:20:16,559
Hm.

489
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:19,319
At my advanced age,

490
00:20:19,599 --> 00:20:21,200
Going out to fight a war,

491
00:20:21,559 --> 00:20:22,839
What if I die?

492
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:23,759
Huh?

493
00:20:24,039 --> 00:20:25,559
If I take the throne now,

494
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:26,759
Then go fight a war,

495
00:20:27,039 --> 00:20:28,519
And then kick the bucket...

496
00:20:28,519 --> 00:20:29,559
No, no, no.

497
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,000
Hey.

498
00:20:31,519 --> 00:20:32,400
Our Daliang Kingdom...

499
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:36,160
Two emperors dead in two months.

500
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:37,799
If word got out,

501
00:20:37,960 --> 00:20:38,559
Wouldn't that

502
00:20:38,839 --> 00:20:40,559
be downright ridiculous?

503
00:20:40,559 --> 00:20:41,880
No, no, no.

504
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,039
Imperial Uncle Liu,

505
00:20:43,039 --> 00:20:45,160
You're truly hilarious.

506
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:47,359
Hey.

507
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:48,440
Where's the wine?

508
00:20:49,039 --> 00:20:50,759
Bring the wine!

509
00:20:50,759 --> 00:20:52,400
Bring the wine!

510
00:20:52,519 --> 00:20:53,680
Pour for them!

511
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,440
Pour them some wine!

512
00:21:03,079 --> 00:21:04,400
Come on, come on.

513
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:05,119
Here.

514
00:21:05,119 --> 00:21:05,960
Little Princess.

515
00:21:06,079 --> 00:21:07,359
Come.

516
00:21:07,519 --> 00:21:08,880
Your Highness, Crown Prince.

517
00:21:10,039 --> 00:21:11,480
Hahahaha!

518
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:16,480
Ah!

519
00:21:16,799 --> 00:21:17,039
Oh dear.

520
00:21:17,039 --> 00:21:19,440
Don't you know your own tolerance for liquor?

521
00:21:19,559 --> 00:21:20,799
Drinking yourself into this state.

522
00:21:20,799 --> 00:21:21,240
Where's the Crown Prince?

523
00:21:21,359 --> 00:21:21,680
Hey.

524
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:22,160
Where is the Crown Prince?

525
00:21:22,359 --> 00:21:24,119
I must protect him. I'm the envoy of Qi.

526
00:21:24,119 --> 00:21:24,920
The Crown Prince

527
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:25,960
is sleeping in the next room.

528
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:27,359
Didn't you take him there yourself?

529
00:21:27,599 --> 00:21:27,920
You...

530
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:28,839
You forgot?

531
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:31,640
Who are you?

532
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:33,400
You...

533
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,319
You kidnapped the Crown Prince!

534
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,559
You wicked woman!

535
00:21:35,759 --> 00:21:36,799
Hey!

536
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:39,000
I'm your Princess, Ouyang Yan!

537
00:21:39,559 --> 00:21:41,599
One more word and I'll kill you.

538
00:21:42,519 --> 00:21:43,359
Ouyang Yan.

539
00:21:46,240 --> 00:21:49,079
I know this girl Ouyang Yan.

540
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:52,079
She's a good girl.

541
00:21:52,519 --> 00:21:54,599
Don't be fooled by all her tough talk.

542
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:58,359
She couldn't even bear to kill Hua Hua.

543
00:21:58,920 --> 00:21:59,759
Hey.

544
00:22:00,359 --> 00:22:02,519
Sit down.

545
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:04,960
Let me tell you.

546
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:06,519
Back then,

547
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:09,559
she gave her own food

548
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:11,880
to Hua Hua every day.

549
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:13,599
And Hua Hua

550
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:15,799
got fatter and fatter,

551
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:17,839
while she got thinner and thinner.

552
00:22:17,839 --> 00:22:19,200
She even stopped growing taller.

553
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:22,960
She grew attached to Hua Hua.

554
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:25,480
When Hua Hua died,

555
00:22:26,359 --> 00:22:28,480
she cried her heart out.

556
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:35,200
Then since you knew she wouldn't kill Hua Hua,

557
00:22:36,079 --> 00:22:38,359
why didn't you just leave her and go?

558
00:22:38,839 --> 00:22:40,039
She can't manage.

559
00:22:41,079 --> 00:22:42,599
That girl,

560
00:22:43,279 --> 00:22:48,720
she's dumb, clumsy, gets lost, and a bit loopy.

561
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:52,039
She got injured all over while training in martial arts.

562
00:22:52,039 --> 00:22:53,599
If she walks too long,

563
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:56,160
her left knee starts hurting.

564
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:58,200
Her stomach's bad too.

565
00:22:58,200 --> 00:23:01,359
Can't eat cold food, won't eat onions.

566
00:23:03,079 --> 00:23:05,359
I have to look after her.

567
00:23:05,599 --> 00:23:08,480
I have to look after her.

568
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:10,200
Oh, man.

569
00:23:10,519 --> 00:23:12,920
I mean, this mission of hers,

570
00:23:12,920 --> 00:23:14,240
the Yan Kingdom...

571
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:20,920
A little girl carrying the whole kingdom on her shoulders.

572
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:24,759
I've already lost Hua Hua.

573
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:27,200
I can't lose her too.

574
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:32,680
Ah.

575
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:34,759
Just like Hua Hua,

576
00:23:35,039 --> 00:23:36,680
she can't do without me.

577
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:39,000
Every other word is about Hua Hua.

578
00:23:39,759 --> 00:23:41,079
A chicken's more important than people?

579
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:45,079
Of course chickens are more important than people.

580
00:23:45,839 --> 00:23:47,160
What a thing to say.

581
00:23:48,799 --> 00:23:50,799
But it depends on the person.

582
00:23:52,519 --> 00:23:54,480
Some people, well...

583
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:55,759
Just...

584
00:23:59,759 --> 00:24:00,880
Father, rest assured.

585
00:24:01,839 --> 00:24:03,359
On this journey,

586
00:24:03,359 --> 00:24:05,160
I will surely succeed in the marriage alliance with the Daliang Kingdom.

587
00:24:05,559 --> 00:24:06,680
To ensure Yan's prosperity.

588
00:24:07,240 --> 00:24:08,279
I, Ouyang Yan,

589
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:10,559
will one day be the Empress of the Daliang Kingdom.

590
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:41,319
Ah.

591
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,000
Why are you here too?

592
00:24:43,359 --> 00:24:44,880
I got up at night and saw Imperial Uncle Liu.

593
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:45,799
You saw it too?

594
00:24:45,799 --> 00:24:46,519
Mm-hmm.

595
00:24:48,839 --> 00:24:50,000
Yue'er.

596
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:52,240
My Prince.

597
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:54,440
Oh my.

598
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:57,279
The chess pieces are already set up.

599
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:06,200
Hasn't Yue'er been dead for ages?

600
00:25:06,759 --> 00:25:08,039
Yet she's still here.

601
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:09,839
Are you stupid?

602
00:25:09,839 --> 00:25:11,440
Even if she were alive, she'd be over fifty.

603
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:13,160
Does she look fifty to you?

604
00:25:14,599 --> 00:25:15,680
Checkmate.

605
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:16,240
Oh-ho.

606
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:17,839
You've really improved.

607
00:25:18,079 --> 00:25:19,359
Hahahaha!

608
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:20,960
Hi!

609
00:25:21,559 --> 00:25:22,839
Yue'er's daughter.

610
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:24,559
Oh my.

611
00:25:24,839 --> 00:25:26,440
Yue'er is Imperial Uncle Liu's consort.

612
00:25:26,440 --> 00:25:28,160
So her daughter is his royal daughter.

613
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:29,839
Have you ever heard he had a daughter?

614
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:33,680
Oh.

615
00:25:35,359 --> 00:25:38,519
So Yue'er had a child with someone else?

616
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:42,359
That's so unfair to Imperial Uncle Liu.

617
00:25:42,799 --> 00:25:43,240
Enough, enough.

618
00:25:43,240 --> 00:25:43,880
I can't deal with you.

619
00:25:43,880 --> 00:25:44,240
Come back with me, quick.

620
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:44,519
Let's go.

621
00:25:44,519 --> 00:25:45,160
We'll talk back there.

622
00:25:46,319 --> 00:25:46,920
Why are you pushing me?

623
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:53,279
Can't you see we're back in his dream?

624
00:25:53,519 --> 00:25:53,880
Huh?

625
00:25:54,519 --> 00:25:55,759
How is that possible?

626
00:25:56,759 --> 00:25:57,960
How much did I drink last night?

627
00:25:58,240 --> 00:26:00,359
Do I look drunk to you right now?

628
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,000
True.

629
00:26:06,359 --> 00:26:07,480
How did this happen?

630
00:26:08,279 --> 00:26:09,279
Oh dear.

631
00:26:09,680 --> 00:26:11,279
He must still be worried about Yue'er.

632
00:26:11,279 --> 00:26:12,480
He wants to lure us all in.

633
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:13,799
Simple, then.

634
00:26:14,519 --> 00:26:16,480
I'll just kill Yue'er again.

635
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:19,240
It won't be that easy this time.

636
00:26:19,359 --> 00:26:21,400
Last time we burst into his dream by surprise.

637
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:22,680
He had no defenses up.

638
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:24,519
But he's already been burned once.

639
00:26:24,519 --> 00:26:25,960
He's bound to be on high alert.

640
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,400
If you fail again,

641
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:28,519
you'll definitely tip him off.

642
00:26:29,519 --> 00:26:30,599
So what do we do?

643
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:33,240
Beat him at his own game.

644
00:26:33,240 --> 00:26:34,000
Let's play dumb for now.

645
00:26:36,559 --> 00:26:37,680
What time is it already?

646
00:26:37,759 --> 00:26:38,920
Why aren't they here yet?

647
00:26:41,359 --> 00:26:42,400
Reporting, My Prince!

648
00:26:42,599 --> 00:26:43,400
Report!

649
00:26:44,519 --> 00:26:45,720
Where's my vanguard army?

650
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:46,720
Why aren't they here yet?

651
00:26:46,759 --> 00:26:48,960
The vanguard ran into bandits on the way.

652
00:26:49,119 --> 00:26:50,680
These bandits are extremely fierce.

653
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:52,519
The vanguard is currently in battle.

654
00:26:52,599 --> 00:26:55,359
They'll be delayed about three days.

655
00:26:56,359 --> 00:26:57,000
Useless!

656
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:58,480
What kind of bandits?

657
00:26:58,599 --> 00:26:59,839
Three days and three nights?

658
00:27:00,279 --> 00:27:01,359
Get out, get out, get out!

659
00:27:01,359 --> 00:27:01,640
Yes, sir.

660
00:27:04,119 --> 00:27:06,000
Who knew such a mishap would occur.

661
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:06,720
So we...

662
00:27:07,079 --> 00:27:09,039
We'll just have to stay a few more days.

663
00:27:09,799 --> 00:27:10,319
Ah.
